title: Flash flooding temporarily trapped Death Valley visitors, rangers
text:
Published By: Las Vegas Review-Journal - Yesterday 
Twenty-three Death Valley National Park visitors and rangers were trapped overnight Monday in flash flooding that damaged several buildings ...
